ffmpeg (0.cvs20060329-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New CVS snapshot.
  * Upstream fixed a double free in img.c (Closes: #351455).
  * Upstream fixed the libvorbisenc dependency in libavcodec.pc
    (Closes: #357352).

