ffmpeg (0.cvs20050918-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * libavcodec/i386/dsputil_mmx.c:
    + Reworked the MMX intrinsics.
  * tests/libav.regression.ref:
    + Minor cosmetic fix to use double-digit numbers in test sequences.
  * debian/control:
